            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1653376203875-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken thigh </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until browned</p><p>Once browned, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add your <strong>orzo</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1653376209381-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
