          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1653376209381-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[650ml]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[1L]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for an initial 5 min</p>",
