    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a small dry pan over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> pine nuts</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1653376221928-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
